    {
      "text": "That's So Raven: Psychic on the Scene is a point-and-click video game based on Disney's That's So Raven television series. In the video game, Raven has to stop the Thompson Theater from closing.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "That's So Raven: Psychic on the Scene é um jogo de 2006 do genero Point Click  baseado na série de TV As Visões da Raven. No jogo, Raven tem que parar o teatro Thompson de fechar.",
      "lang": "pt",
      "source": "wikipedia_pt"
    },
    {
      "text": "『That's So Raven: Psychic on the Scene』は、ディズニーのテレビシリーズ『That's So Raven』を原作としたポイント＆クリック形式のビデオゲームです。このゲームでは、レイヴンがトンプソン劇場が閉館するのを阻止するという目的を果たすことになります。",
